// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0394 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: e48b68e2-4547-5b41-ace9-2a8ba123d1d6

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04-ESM*")
